                    <li>Malic acid: Derived from apples and other fruits, but also found in citrus fruits</li>
                    <li>Tartaric acid: Derived from grapes, but also found in citrus fruits
                    </ul> 
                    <p>The natural origin of citrus fruit acids makes them a popular choice for individuals seeking plant-based and eco-friendly skincare ingredients. However, it is essential to note that citrus fruit acids can cause skin sensitivity and irritation in some individuals, particularly when used in high concentrations or on sensitive skin types.</p>
